	<h2 id="csp-id-0d65aa2b-1ec9-4712-beee-265f79c0cb97">Discover our products</h2>
<p id="csp-id-7ecb8328-0454-4b59-8755-e9db8b5f1275">Bank of America has checking accounts, savings accounts and credit cards, while Merrill has investing accounts - all to help you reach your financial goals.<br>
</p>
<p id="csp-id-33a324ed-219e-404a-a7e2-70e98250c6f5"><a href="https://info.bankofamerica.com/en/student-banking/getting-started.html" target="_self">See Products &amp; Services</a></p>

